text: "Dat Stick" (styled as "Dat $tick") is the debut single by Indonesian hip hop recording artist Rich Brian, previously known as Rich Chigga. It was released on March 11, 2016. The song was produced by Ananta Vinnie. ==Background== Rich Brian released the song on March 11, 2016 on streaming services. ==Music video== The video of Dat Stick was uploaded to Brian's YouTube channel on February 22, 2016, which became quickly viral over the internet. Rappers such as Desiigner, Cam'ron, Ghostface Killah, 21 Savage, MadeinTYO and many more have reacted to the video. Rich Brian also released a video for a remixed version featuring Ghostface Killah and Pouya. ==Remix== On October 12, 2016, the official remix of "Dat Stick" was released, which features American rappers Ghostface Killah and Pouya. ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" style="text-align:center;" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2016) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- | scope="row"| US Bubbling Under R&B;/Hip-Hop Singles (Billboard) | 4 |- |} ==Certifications== ==References== ==External links== *Lyrics of this song at Genius Category:2016 singles Category:2016 songs Category:Rich Brian songs
